Nu!

243
00:17:31.820 --> 00:17:33.740
Deschide ușa, te rog!

244
00:17:34.490 --> 00:17:36.820
Mamă!

245
00:17:38.770 --> 00:17:44.333
Alfred Corner Cafe
Palak Book Center


246
00:17:45.160 --> 00:17:46.950
Uite, bea niște apă.

247
00:17:52.620 --> 00:17:55.280
